.req
.reqmap - Requirements map. Used when creating a new entry. A simple description of field constraints, such as "not empty"

.form - Description in computer readable form of the HTML form in a .template and the database table(s) and fields associated with it.

template/*.html
.template - An HTML template, specifically an HTML::Template.

.rmap
.report - Like .form, but for the report builder/query results pages which have many different and special requirements.

.yml - YAML markup code. In practice nearly all files are in YAML, this just means it's a generic format of some kind.

.cmps - A list of SQL comparisions.
